snippet: Amanda Blumenherst and the L.P.G.A. rookie leader Moriya Jutanugarn shot five-under 66s to top the leader board in the ShopRite L.P.G.A. Classic.
abstract: Three-time NCAA player of the year Amanda Blumenherst and rookie leader Moriya Jutanugarn share first-round lead at ShopRite LPGA Classic; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Amanda Blumenherst and the L.P.G.A. rookie leader Moriya Jutanugarn shot five-under 66s to top the leader board in the ShopRite L.P.G.A. Classic.
